				\begin{document}$0.163 \pm 0.008$\end{document}, based on the estimates of Konopliv et al. 2016 and Genova et al. 2016) ruled out earlier results in the range of k2=0.12–0.13\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
