As indicated in Sect. 3.4 and described in detail in Mimoun et al. (2017), the pressure noise associated with the low rigidity surface deformation will likely be the limiting factor at both long periods (T>15–20s\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
