				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$i^{2}=-1$\end{document}) to 0.70 Hz. The feedback is nevertheless strong enough to accommodate unstable free frequencies. The three VBBs can therefore operate in a non-nominal mode within ±2.5∘\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
