To confirm this, an SP sensor unit was placed into a magnetic test coil and the response to a 1.5 mT change in field recorded. The resulting highest sensitivity in any orientation was determined as 0.15m/s2/T\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
