				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\mbox{vibrations} + \mbox{thermal cycles}$\end{document}) and also after integration in the sphere. The main parameters screened during the test program were: 
Pendulum eigenfrequencies: decreasing eigenfrequencies will increase the mechanical gain and the signal-to-noise ratio with a 1/f02\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
