				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$1/f _{0} ^{2}$\end{document} law. Expected variations are ±10%\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\pm 10\%$\end{document} (0.5%/∘C\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
